HEADWORD: Chiasma
<hw>Chi*as"ma</hw> <pr>(k⟦isl⟧*⟦acr⟧z"m⟦adot⟧)</pr>, }</mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. <ets>chiasma</ets>, fr. Gr. <grk>chi`asma</grk>
